flowchart LR
  API["HTTP API: POST /events"] -->|key=device_id| MAIN["Kafka topic: events"]
  MAIN --> PROC["Processor / Consumer"]
  RETRY["Kafka topic: events.retry"] --> PROC
  PROC --> BA["Batch accumulator"]
  BA --> SINK["Primary sink: data/events.jsonl"]
  PROC -->|normal success path| SINK
  PROC -->|retry path: transient failure + retries left| RETRY
  PROC -->|DLQ path: permanent failure or retries exhausted| DLQ["DLQ sink: data/dlq.jsonl"]
  PROC --> LEDGER["Idempotency ledger (optional)"]
  API --> APIS["GET /stats (api-local)"]
  PROC --> CDBG["GET /consumer/debug/state (consumer-local)"]
